title: ChronicCareIQ
description: Your doctor or hospital may have asked you to download "ChronicCareIQ" to assist in the on-going management of your care or as you transition home from the hospital. This app is exclusively for patients of participating health care providers and systems. After downloading it, follow the instructions on the information sheet you were given at the office or hospital. To learn more, please visit ChronicCareIQ.com or call the number on your information sheet.
